{"tid":973963,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Deliveroo既人麻煩同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T16:34:29.000Z","uid":165198,"like":124,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4729ab7c6e4cb69145cf832e33d15ed7fdf6845b","tid":973963,"uid":165198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"9點鐘落單叫野食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/08/214750_bda06452460cbfd7f3e16c01b89af293.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2F214750_bda06452460cbfd7f3e16c01b89af293.png&h=74a7c1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦 我開netflix睇監獄風雲等野食到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/08/214825_008b09491a5a9910f0e3b64ccf89496f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2F214825_008b09491a5a9910f0e3b64ccf89496f.png&h=7fce9f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等左就黎9個字都知唔對路，點知無啦啦話訂單已送到<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/08/214911_f49d4b479e247eba743f14a3636dd0e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2F214911_f49d4b479e247eba743f14a3636dd0e4.png&h=86b50686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌冇人打比我冇人黎過，同我講送到？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/08/215001_52e22504ac6614c70b23d210cecdf6b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2F215001_52e22504ac6614c70b23d210cecdf6b5.png&h=12b4c2a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去客服嘈佢唔理，再打去先同我講個司機已經唔見左，我退番款比你，我屌你老母，係咪我唔打比你就當冇事發生過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家下仲要on99自己煮麵食，下次我叫熊貓都唔撚叫你。"},{"pid":"6896556fb6bcf9712697f1282efaba6b889cb173","tid":973963,"uid":185328,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"404 not found"},{"pid":"47393fa7174a8a0932ab5ceea50be0b50e933e77","tid":973963,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"Deliver嗚~"},{"pid":"8848e64bd08d24d6cdbb474a7b9569c74c2a78e8","tid":973963,"uid":73232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"家陣deliveroo啲步兵真係無咩質素"},{"pid":"b4335c9e8dabdbb5ada32f8bd90b94d414db91a7","tid":973963,"uid":165198,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"真係唔係話我小氣，睇監獄風雲發哥皇家飯食左幾碟我都未有得食，打去竟然同我講個司機唔見左，真識做生意"},{"pid":"a8081f4ac1e28dd4d5ea0fe69263a9b23887ce1e","tid":973963,"uid":14478,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:58.000Z","msg":"Food panda 連車手都冇cfm唔到訂單"},{"pid":"307c8eca455f2b955118a4cbf109916ba8a6ade1","tid":973963,"uid":196924,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"渣打里數卡廣告?"},{"pid":"c2b6b684e7d1d0ea62d0f6dd411e21781648864d","tid":973963,"uid":93479,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b4335c9e8dabdbb5ada32f8bd90b94d414db91a7","tid":973963,"uid":165198,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"真係唔係話我小氣，睇監獄風雲發哥皇家飯食左幾碟我都未有得食，打去竟然同我講個司機唔見左，真識做生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"周潤發都食得好過你"},{"pid":"e5796be4c16325ba6dd3e996c53d6a87a51fc092","tid":973963,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔好咁懶 落街買啦<img src=\"/